title: Weds Post Show (04-06-22)
itunes:title: Weds Post Show (04-06-22)
description:
Amy starts by revealing the pain that has been bothering her. Morgan has us play a fun Facebook game to get to know us. We talk about stories from the show getting back to our significant others. We play a game called Alive or Not Alive that leads to a discussion about how long life is. It gets deep when we start diving into life expectations.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
